Hellplague:
 
The femme listened for a moment, then got up and went looking for him, to see what was bothering Celeron so much.  
 
"Celeron, what is it that is bothering you so much?  I might be able to help," she said as she looked for the other bot.

rm2kmidi <kraftlos@...> wrote:
"I guess that will have to do, for now....." said Celeron in a rather
tired-sounding voice, as he proceded to march back to the storage room
and retrieve the item.

He broke open the crate with an unnecessary amount of force, he
doubted that it would ever close again.  Then he snatched the scanner
and took it with him to a dark corner where he could examine his vital
functions...


"HA!  Is that all you got?  You boasted such power, such skill!  Where is your power and skill now?  You disappoint me, ha ha ha haa!"
